dct_title_s: Asia-Pacific LNG map / Petroleum Economist Cartographic ; produced by Petroleum Economist in association with Pavilin Energy ; designed by K. Fuller and P. Bush. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: "Published May 2018"--Cover panel Relief and depths shown by shading and gradient tints. Accompanies: Petroleum Economist, v.85, no. 6, July/August 2018. Shows gas fields, gas pipelines, export plants, import terminals. Includes statistical charts and graphs, 4 insets and 1 ancillary map. 4 insets: Japan -- Singapore -- Australia North West Shelf -- Australia Curtis Island. Ancillary map: Natural gas, trade movements of LNG in Asia 2016. On verso: Panel title, publisher's advertisements, and color illustrations.
